#
# az - Azure CLI
#
# https://docs.microsoft.com/ja-jp/cli/azure/reference-index?view=azure-cli-latest
#

az login

# Show information of login user
az account show

## extension

az extension list
az extension add --name <extension>
az extension update --name <extension>
az extension remove --name <extension>

## IoT

az iot hub device-identity connection-string show --hub-name <iot hub name> --device-id <device id> --output table
